DESCRIPTION:Join Deaf artist and practitioner Zoya  for a guided walkthrough of the exhibition warrior garments. \n\nReflecting on her journey of resilience\, passion and her aim to create inclusive spaces for the Deaf community\, Zoya brings forward the voices of Deaf women through her interpretation of the exhibition. \n
DTEND:20260620T220000Z
DTSTART:20260620T213000Z
SUMMARY:Deaf Artist POV Walkthrough: Zoya
